ygData.msgSnippet: Rangers also have an underwater breathing spell ... From: Joel Thronburg  To:  Sent: Wednesday, July 07, 1999
ygData.messageBody:
Rangers also have an underwater breathing spell


----- Original Message -----
From: Joel Thronburg <jthronburg@...>
To: <EQCheats@onelist.com>
Sent: Wednesday, July 07, 1999 1:34 PM
Subject: Re: [EQCheats] Dagnor's Cauldron


> From: Joel Thronburg <jthronburg@...>
>
> There was a bard that was recruting folks to go to Kedge last night on
> the Rathe. He went inside solo earlier and said that he was the only
> person in the zone. It is just a really tough place since you have to
> have water breathing, bard songs or Fishbone earrings to survive long
> enough to fight.
>
> > -----Original Message-----
> > From: Tony Cawthorne [SMTP:tac1@...]

> > In the water there somewhere in Dagnor's is the entrance to another
> > dungeon
> > called "Kedge Keep" the entire dungeon is underwater and the entrance
> > is

> >
> > Quindinar
